# Metasploit: TCP SYN port scan (triggers NIDS port-scan module when traffic hits the sniffed interface).
# Before running: in msfconsole, set RHOSTS to the VICTIM IP (not 127.0.0.1 unless you sniff lo).
#
#   msfconsole -r /home/kali/Desktop/nids_edit_metasploit/metasploit_lab/portscan_syn.rc
#
# Or paste by hand after editing RHOSTS:

use auxiliary/scanner/portscan/syn
setg RHOSTS 192.168.56.101
set PORTS 1-512
set THREADS 20
run
